Dictionary maintenance functions:

Generate list of words with pictures

cd "content/dictionary images"
ls | grep -v thumb | sed 's/\.jpg//' > ~/Desktop/dictionary_pictures

Generate list of all dictionary words

mongoexport --db=looma --collection=dictionary --projection="{'en':1}" --out="dictionary_words"
Sort -u dictionary_words > dictionary_words_sorted

Generate list of words without pictures

comm -23  dictionary_words_sorted dictionary_pictures > dictionary_words_without_pictures
